you, O the father of the guiding leaders. Sufficient for you is the nobility and lineage which Allah has rendered you and enough for you is the honour and esteem that He has granted you. Peace be on you, O the one noble of existence. Peace be on you, O the friend of worshipped one. Peace be on you, O the protector of the Promised Prophet. Peace be on you, O the one who was granted a son, who is the best of the new-born ones.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "INSHA-ALLAH COMING SOON", "Urdu": "انشاء اللہ ترجمہ جلد آرہا ہے", "RArabic": "AS-SALAAMO A’LAIKA YAA SAYYEDAL BAT-HAAA-E WABNA RAEE-SE-HAA. AS-SALAAMO A’LAIKA YAA WAARE-SAL KA’BA-TE BA’DA TAA SEESE-HAA. AS-SALAAMO A’LAIKA YAA KAAFELA RAOOLIL LAAHE. AS-SALAAMO A’LAIKA YAA HAAFE-ZA DEENIL LAAHE. AS-SALAAMO A’LAIKA YAA A’MMAL MUSTAFAA. AS-SALAAMO A’LAIKA YAA ABAL MURTAZAA. AS-SALAAMO A’LAIKA YAA WAALE-DAL AIMMA-TIL HODAA KAFAA-KA BE-MAA AWLAA-KAL LAAHO SHARA-FAN WA NASA-BAN WA HASBO-KA BE-MAA A’TAA-KAL LAAHO A’ZZAN WA HASA-BAN. AS-SALAAMO A’LAIKA YAA SHARA-FAL WOJOO-DE. AS-SALAAMO A’LAIKA YAA WALIYYAL MA’BOODE. AS-SALAAMO A’LAIKA YAA HAARE-SAN NABIYYIL MAW-OO’DE.", "ArabicText1": "اَلسَّلَامُ عَلَيْكَ يَاسَيِّدَ الْبَطْحَآءِ وَابْنَ رَئِيْسِهَا۔ اَلسَّلَامُ عَلَيْكَ يَاوَارِثَ الْكَعْبَةِ بَعْدَ تَاْسِيْسِهَا۔ اَلسَّلَامُ عَلَيْكَ يَاكَافِلَ رَسُوْلِ اللهِ۔ اَلسَّلَامُ عَلَيْكَ يَاحَافِظَ دِيْنِ اللهِ۔ اَلسَّلَامُ عَلَيْكَ يَاعَمَّ الْمُصْطَفٰى۔ اَلسَّلَامُ عَلَيْكَ يَااَبَا الْمُرْتَضٰى۔ اَلسَّلَامُ عَلَيْكَ يَاوَالِدَ الْاَئِمَّةِ الْهُدٰى كَفَاكَ بِمَا اَوْلَاكَ اللهُ شَرَفًا وَّ نَسَبًا وَّ حَسْبُكَ بِمَا اَعْطَاكَ اللهُ عِزًّا وَّ حَسَبًا۔ اَلسَّلَامُ عَلَيْكَ يَاشَرَفَ الْوُجُوْدِ۔ اَلسَّلَامُ عَلَيْكَ يَاوَلِىَّ الْمَعْبُوْدِ۔ اَلسَّلَامُ عَلَيْكَ يَاحَارِسَ النَّبِىِّ الْمَوْعُوْدِ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1010317, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "Peace be on you, O the one who was designated for a chaste, pure, purified and lofty son (Ali) whose name is derived from that of Allah’s (Ali). Congratulations be to you for your son who is the satisfied one of the Apostles, the brother of the Apostle, the husband of Batool (Janabe Fatema) and the everdrawn sword of Allah. Again congratulations be to you for your son whose position with Mohammad al-Mustafa is like the one with Hazrat Haaroon had with Hazrat Moosa. Congratulations be to you for your son who is a partner in prophethood. The chosen one for brotherhood (with the Holy Prophet). The removal of sorrow, the leader of the nation and the father of the Imams. Congratulations be to you, for your son who is the distributor of Paradise and Hell, the Bounty of Allah upon the righteous and His Wrath upon the debauchers. Peace be on you and on him and on them all (Imams) and the Mercy of Allah and His Blessings.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": "AS-SALAAMO A’LAIKA YAA MAN ROZE-KA WALADOON HOWA KHAIRO MAWLOO-DIN. AS-SALAAMO A’LAIKA YAA MAN KHUSSE BIL WALA-DIZ ZAKIY-YIT TAAHE-RIL A’LIY-YISH TUQQAS MOHU MINAL A’LIYYE, HANEE-AL LAKA SUMMA HANEE-AL LAKA MIN WALA-DIN HOWAL MURTAZAA MIN RASOOLIN WA A-KHUR RASOOLE WA ZAWJAL BATOO-LE WA SAIFUL LAAHIL MASLOO-LO HANEE-AL LAKA SUMMA HANEE-AL LAKA MIN WALA-DIN HOWA MIM MOHAMMADE-NIL MUSTAFAA BE-MANZE-LA-TE HAAROO-NA MIN MOOSAA. HANEE-AL LAKA MIN WALA-DIN HOWA SHAREE-KUN NABUWWA-TE WAL MAKHSOO-SO BIL O-KHOO-WA-TE WA KAASHE-FUL GHUMMA-TE WA IMAAMUL UMMA-TE WA ABUL AIMMA-TE, HANEE-AL LAKA MIN WALA-DIN HOWA QASEE-MUL JANNATE WAN NAARE WA NE’MA-TUL LAAHE A’LAL ABRAA-RE WA NAQEMA-TUL LAAHE A’LAL FUJ-JAARE. AS-SALAAMO A’LAIKA WA A’LAI-HE WA A’LAI-HIM AJMA-EE’NA WA RAHMA-TUL LAAHE WA BARA-KAATO-HU.", "ArabicText1": "اَلسَّلَامُ عَلَيْكَ يَامَنْ رُزِقَ وَلَدٌ هُوَ خَيْرُ مَوْلُوْدٍ۔ اَلسَّلَامُ عَلَيْكَ يَامَنْ خُصِّصَ بِالْوَلَدِ الزَّكِىِّ الطَّاهِرِ الْمُطَهَّرِ الْعَلِىٍّ اشْتُقَّ اسْمُهٗ مِنَ الْعَلِىِّ، هَنِيْئًا لَّكَ ثُمَّ هَنِيْئًا لَّكَ مِنْ وَّلَدٍ هُوَ الْمُرْتَضٰى مِنْ رَسُوْلٍ وَّ اَخُ الرَّسُوْلِ وَزَوْجُ الْبَتُوْلِ وَسَيْفُ اللهِ الْمَسْلُوْلُ هَنِيْئًا لَّكَ ثُمَّ هَنِيْئًا لَّكَ مِنْ وَّلَدٍ هُوَ مِنْ مُّحَمَّدِ ", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": " نِ", "ArabicText2": "الْمُصْطَفٰى بِمَنْزِلَةِ هَارُوْنَ مِنْ مُوْسٰى۔ هَنِيْئًا لَّكَ مِنْ وَّلَدٍ هُوَ شَرِيْكُ النُّبُوَّةِ وَالْمَخْصُوْصُ بِالْاُخُوَّةِ وَكَاشِفُ الْغُمَّةِ وَاِمَامُ الْاُمَّةِ وَاَبُوْ الْاَئِمَّةِ، هَنِيْئًا لَّكَ مِنْ وَّ لَدٍ هُوَ قَسِيْمُ الْجَنَّةِ وَالنَّارِ وَنِعْمَةُ اللهِ عَلَى الْاَبْرَارِ وَنَقِمَةُ اللهِ عَلَى الْفُجَّارِ۔ اَلسَّلَامُ عَلَيْكَ وَعَلَيْهِ وَعَلَيْهِمْ اَجْمَعِيْنَ وَرَحْمَةُ اللهِ وَ بَرَكَاتُهٗ۔", "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13